#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.111"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.111:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.111:0.2"
msgid "11. Samaṇasaññāvagga"
msgstr "11. Perceptions for Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.111:0.3"
msgid "111. Paṭhamaasekhasutta"
msgstr "111. An Adept (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.111:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and "
"said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.111:2.1"
msgid "“‘Asekho asekho’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this person called ‘an adept’."

msgctxt "an10.111:2.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā bhante, bhikkhu asekho hotī”ti?"
msgstr "How is an adept mendicant defined?”"

msgctxt "an10.111:2.3"
msgid ""
"“Idha, bhikkhu, bhikkhu asekhāya sammādiṭṭhiyā samannāgato hoti, asekhena "
"sammāsaṅkappena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāvācāya samannāgato hoti, "
"asekhena sammākammantena samannāgato hoti, asekhena sammāājīvena samannāgato "
"hoti, asekhena sammāvāyāmena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāsatiyā "
"samannāgato hoti, asekhena sammāsamādhinā samannāgato hoti, asekhena "
"sammāñāṇena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāvimuttiyā samannāgato hoti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, it’s when a mendicant has an adept’s right view, right thought, "
"right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right "
"mindfulness, right immersion, right knowledge, and right freedom."

msgctxt "an10.111:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhu, bhikkhu asekho hotī”ti."
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is an adept.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.111:2.5"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
